name: Rebirth.
description: It is that time again. Throw away the old, the unbearable, it is gonna be ok. Love is always gonna set you free. Have compassion to your process. Forgive yourself. The future starts in the present. My Love is deep. As my soul. So as yours. Love. Live. Laugh? Damn i became a cliche. But i'm in love with new perspectives. Thank you.
